other_tests.findings: Adenoid cystic carcinoma of the maxilla with predominant cribriform pattern and focal perineural lymphatic invasion.
Metastatic disease in the manubrium and the right ninth and left tenth ribs; diffusely progressive disease.
other_tests.changes_over_time: Progressed to multiple pulmonary nodules, bilaterally and predominantly in the lower lung regions, with mild hilar lymphadenopathy.
